#: includes/woocommerce/class-product.php:271
#: includes/woocommerce/class-product.php:679
msgid "Start date event"
msgstr "Fecha de inicio del evento"

#: includes/woocommerce/class-product.php:274
#: includes/woocommerce/class-product.php:682
msgid ""
"Set this to have this printed on the ticket and prevent too early redeemed "
"tickets. Tickets can be redeemed from that day on."
msgstr ""
"Si se establece, se imprimirá en el ticket y evitará canjes demasiado "
"tempranos. Los tickets se pueden canjear a partir de ese día."

#: includes/woocommerce/class-product.php:280
#: includes/woocommerce/class-product.php:688
msgid "Start time"
msgstr "Hora de inicio"

#: includes/woocommerce/class-product.php:282
#: includes/woocommerce/class-product.php:299
#: includes/woocommerce/class-product.php:690
#: includes/woocommerce/class-product.php:707
msgid "Set this to have this printed on the ticket."
msgstr "Establezca esto para que se imprima en el ticket."

#: includes/woocommerce/class-product.php:288
#: includes/woocommerce/class-product.php:696
msgid "End date event"
msgstr "Fecha de finalización del evento"

#: includes/woocommerce/class-product.php:291
#: includes/woocommerce/class-product.php:699
msgid ""
"Set this to have this printed on the ticket and prevent later the ticket to "
"be still valid. Tickets cannot be redeemed after that day."
msgstr ""
"Si se establece, se imprimirá en el ticket y evitará que el ticket siga "
"siendo válido después. Los tickets no se pueden canjear después de ese día."

#: includes/woocommerce/class-product.php:297
#: includes/woocommerce/class-product.php:705
msgid "End time"
msgstr "Hora de finalización"

#: includes/woocommerce/class-product.php:306
msgid "Date is for all variants"
msgstr "La fecha se aplica a todas las variantes"

#: includes/woocommerce/class-product.php:307
msgid ""
"Activate this, to have the entered date printed on all product variants. No "
"effect on simple products."
msgstr ""
"Active esto para que la fecha introducida se imprima en todas las variantes "
"del producto. Sin efecto en productos simples."

#: includes/woocommerce/class-product.php:318
msgid "Customer can choose the day"
msgstr "El cliente puede elegir el día"

#: includes/woocommerce/class-product.php:319
msgid ""
"Activate this, to allow your customer to choose a date. If this option is "
"active it will use the start and end date as limits, if provided. And use "
"only the start and end time setting. If the start and end time is not set, "
"then the entrance is allowed from 00:00 till 23:59."
msgstr ""
"Active esto para permitir que su cliente elija una fecha. Si esta opción "
"está activa, utilizará las fechas de inicio y fin como límites, si se "
"proporcionan. Y utilizará solo la configuración de hora de inicio y fin. Si "
"no se establece la hora de inicio y fin, la entrada se permite de 00:00 a "
"23:59."

#: includes/woocommerce/class-product.php:324
msgid "Only one date picker"
msgstr "Solo un selector de fecha"

#: includes/woocommerce/class-product.php:325
msgid ""
"If this option is active, then only one date is allowed per purchase of this "
"product. If your customer buys 2 or more of this ticket, than only one date "
"picker will be shown for all the tickets. The default is to display for each "
"product in the cart one separated date picker."
msgstr ""
"Si esta opción está activa, solo se permite una fecha por compra de este "
"producto. Si su cliente compra 2 o más de esta entrada, se mostrará solo un "
"selector de fecha para todos los tickets. El valor predeterminado es mostrar "
"para cada producto en el carrito un selector de fecha separado."

#: includes/woocommerce/class-product.php:332
msgid "Choose which days to exclude"
msgstr "Elija qué días excluir"

#: includes/woocommerce/class-product.php:333
msgid ""
"To select more than one, hold down the CTRL key. The selected days cannot be "
"choosen by your customer in date chooser."
msgstr ""
"Para seleccionar más de uno, mantenga presionada la tecla CTRL. Los días "
"seleccionados no pueden ser elegidos por su cliente en el selector de fecha."

#: includes/woocommerce/class-product.php:337
msgid "Monday"
msgstr "Lunes"

#: includes/woocommerce/class-product.php:338
msgid "Tuesday"
msgstr "Martes"

#: includes/woocommerce/class-product.php:339
msgid "Wednesday"
msgstr "Miércoles"

#: includes/woocommerce/class-product.php:340
msgid "Thursday"
msgstr "Jueves"

#: includes/woocommerce/class-product.php:341
msgid "Friday"
msgstr "Viernes"

#: includes/woocommerce/class-product.php:342
msgid "Saturday"
msgstr "Sábado"

#: includes/woocommerce/class-product.php:343
msgid "Sunday"
msgstr "Domingo"

#: includes/woocommerce/class-product.php:351
msgid "Offset days for start date"
msgstr "Días de compensación para la fecha de inicio"

#: includes/woocommerce/class-product.php:354
msgid ""
"This will set how many days to skip before you allow your customer to choose "
"a date. 0 means starting from the same day, 1 means from tomorrow on and so "
"on. If you set a start date, the the start date will be considered as a "
"minimum starting date."
msgstr ""
"Esto establece cuántos días saltar antes de permitir que su cliente elija "
"una fecha. 0 significa comenzar desde el mismo día, 1 significa desde mañana "
"en adelante, etc. Si establece una fecha de inicio, la fecha de inicio se "
"considerará como una fecha de inicio mínima."

#: includes/woocommerce/class-product.php:361
msgid "Offset days for end date"
msgstr "Días de compensación para la fecha de fin"

#: includes/woocommerce/class-product.php:364
msgid ""
"This will set how many days in the future do you allow your customer to "
"choose a date. 0 unlimited into the future, 1 means until tomorrow on and so "
"on. If a end date is set, then this option is ignored and the end date is "
"used."
msgstr ""
"Esto establece cuántos días en el futuro permite que su cliente elija una "
"fecha. 0 ilimitado en el futuro, 1 significa hasta mañana en adelante, etc. "
"Si se establece una fecha de fin, esta opción se ignora y se utiliza la "
"fecha de fin."

#: includes/woocommerce/class-product.php:370
msgid "Label for the date picker"
msgstr "Etiqueta para el selector de fecha"

#: includes/woocommerce/class-product.php:371
#: includes/woocommerce/class-product.php:470
